HAPPIEST BIRTHDAY TO OUR BABYGIRL VICTORIA! I am so honored to be your momma. You bring so much joy to our lives! You continue to inspire us daily. You are such a great light in this world. What a great weekend it was! I had the honor of making my first vendor appearance at the She Speaks Power Women’s Conference, orchestrated by the wonderful Teri (@aubrijai). Surrounded by so many strong, bold, and creative women, I felt truly humbled and honored to be a part of this incredible experience. Teri, you truly outdid yourself 👏🏽👏🏽👏🏽 Thank you for being obedient and organizing such a spectacular event 💪🏽

To everyone who stopped by the Earring Envy table, thank you for your kind words, your encouragement, and your purchases. Your belief and trust in us mean the world. Earring Envy is here to stay, and I couldn’t be more grateful 🙌🏽

Shoutout to @mommyzjourney for having my back and making the trip to Texas with me. I’m blessed with the most amazing friends 🙌🏽

And @joshua_dwain, I couldn’t have asked for a better partner. Your unwavering support means everything to me. Thank you for always having my back, my side, and every corner. I love you! #iwillretiremyhusband

I’m filled with gratitude for every opportunity that comes my way, and for each and every one of you who love my designs and support Envy 💪🏽💪🏽💪🏽

God, you are so good to me, Thank you !
